Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,2,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}字幕調校: {\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HCFE96F&\b0}星辰@CMCT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電影真的很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它是有自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果導演能拍出一部精彩作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它肯定會比導演長命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電影又很詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演拍的東西想觀眾明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們偏偏看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有的沒拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們卻又看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電影是導演的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實是導演創造了夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是夢創造了導演？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去看了你拍的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都不明白你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在…拍些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我也搞不懂…你在說…說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…總是…要頂嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…你什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道 監製的權力比導演大？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只知道你說話結巴 不知道你哪樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}九號是我的幸運號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每當我走到第九步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的靈感就會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可每到八步半 你就來打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正忙著拍戲呀 大監製
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要煩我行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖 把那盞大燈給我掛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照住大監製的頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大監製
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道在拍攝現場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演的權力最大？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}輪不到你作主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掛上去 照醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…這樣說話…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在就炒你魷魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒力啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}監製 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事…沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演出事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演 導演…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演有事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 導演暈倒了 - 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 出什麼事了？ - 召救護車 快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 怎麼辦？ - 導演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導演有事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 導演暈倒了 - 召救護車 導演暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}召救護車 快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼地方？我怎會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我成了鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這世界哪有鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的電影還沒拍完 怎會上映呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裏就是鴻圖樓 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會給"人情"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有喜帖都不讓進 什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是來喝喜酒 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別離開婆婆半步 聽到嗎？阿仔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裏 斗大的字寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鴻圖樓樓上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就是嘛 鴻圖樓樓上那層嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是來喝喜酒 又不是來打劫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就對了 樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妹 這個適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直都嫁不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各位俊男美女 大家晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常開心 大家能夠蒞臨東哥的喜宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚 我們將在九大行星及嫦娥的見證下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起體驗這對百年好合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事不宜遲 我們馬上請大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍移玉步到後面的迴旋樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢慢升上來和大家一起用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 一個接一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不許插隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}七層樓 想累死人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 多謝人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼只給一千二百？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩個人一千二 你開玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 我們這兒有人情價目表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明碼實價的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個人頭不低於五百塊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八百塊以下要自帶椅子和飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的椅子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那請你進去時別佔人家的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 沒有椅子 怎麼吃呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我細雞 只是幫東哥做兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有什麼話直接跟東哥說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎麼說也是阿東的三叔公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公 請你快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要擋著街坊朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼急幹什麼 急著去死呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}插隊？喝喜酒也要插隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 肥姨 看來你會比他先餓死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我為什麼會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很簡單 你這兒才一份人情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定要讓給小孩吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣你還不餓死？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子還不到一米五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上大酒店吃東西都不用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你傻的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企直 貼牆 抬高頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你企直 抬高頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽不懂中文嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆教我 量身高時別站太直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到了 肥姨 過了一米五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}政府是不是算一個人頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}政府說的話你也相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭髮也算嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是超過一米五…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果頭髮也算 我恤起頭髮也比姚明高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}香港小姐頭髮那麼長 豎起來不就兩米多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是蠻橫不講理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然 看我這份量就是橫著來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看到的 我是橫著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}換作是我就不收錢了 省點吧笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊 怕你呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…不能不收錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請留言…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請你吃榴蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿東
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能快一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我給他剪了頭髮 你要給錢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？你才四百？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你留著坐車回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得把人情放進箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊有個價目表 都給我核對好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你核對了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天好帥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好位置在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}招呼不周 先打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝你百年好合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝 請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人情給了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年抱兩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝 這麼大了 隨便坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊才是好位…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事 東哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那妞到現在還不出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不接電話 婚宴就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有新娘怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 這主意是我出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可你才給我幾天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一面要發帖邀請人來喝你的喜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊呢 還要幫你找個妞來充新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你指名道姓要那妞兒來做新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在她放你鴿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這到底關我什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大 現在是你欠人家錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說了 現在沒新娘 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正是假結婚 幹嘛要那麼認真？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現成有個妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長頭髮 大胸脯 厚嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你連我嬤嬤也叫來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做戲做全套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿東
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤真想不到 可以親眼看著你娶媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的開心極了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你爸媽如果還在 也會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把你撫養成人到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最精彩就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這玉鐲是我給孫媳婦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你快帶我去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她人呢？我們去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在補妝呀 嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁她忙著補妝 我們打麻將等她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 先打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好呀 打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤交給我照顧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿東沒跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我打麻將 很出名的 - 謝謝 招呼不周 隨便坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}順利村第三座 分組第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼厲害 我是第四座冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過是幫我媽抽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公 你喜歡摸就帶兩隻回家摸個飽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 是這只四索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼多西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你老…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關公保佑 終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牽住人家的手 見嬤嬤呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤 起床啦 嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孫媳婦來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 這件嫁衣是她親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多賢慧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就隨便給封紅包意思意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這水型人格的面相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛好可彌補阿東五行欠水的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是天生夫妻相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你紅包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你叫什麼名？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫多多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定會好好照顧阿東
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是皆大歡喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們請便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東哥 我還有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤 她不僅漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看她的屁股 就像我年輕時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定好生養
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 剛才打電話給你 怎那麼吵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打電話給我幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 你一直不接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點害怕你會爽約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我答應你就不會爽約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才 我回錦田的祖屋取這件嫁衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 手工多精緻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我家傳之寶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那對龍爪好威猛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 吃了這餐晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚宴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚有東西吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你等等 細雞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃？才那麼一丁點"人情"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫他們吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這麼多人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是呀 你說你的親戚都是稻草蓋珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還說都是很闊綽 可都不來呀大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫他們吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我真要吃屎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屎也得花錢買呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這回連屎也沒得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有個餿主意 保證比屎還便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}舉起雙手 舉起雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嚇鬼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你妨礙我幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起火啦 火燒後巷呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火警 火警 快跑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 當心點 - 嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿東
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都走了 散席了 你回家休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也早點休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就只有一個乖孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要好好照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東哥 我送嬤嬤回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 等等 等等嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤 我們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像忘了樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會不會呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤 鐲子你收好 不要給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你的 你收好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別這樣 嬤嬤 你留著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過幾天我們來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到時再給我們 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不我來保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得…最近真的好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醫生說我有腫瘤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼瘤 你死前可不可以先送我嬤嬤回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這沒問題 你是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤 我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 今晚別太累 - 再見嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}累了就找我來幫忙 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這棵不就是蝎子鳳梨 很罕見呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}識貨 它叫秀蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有那個 它叫秀月 中間的叫瑩瑩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後面那棵叫茱安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你泡花呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抽煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少抽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是他的老大 很能打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年輕時就能打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在較多打飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在香港 做廢青很難找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我打算先歇著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近主要看看書 種些花草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你不就變成文化古惑仔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我也很喜歡種花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前還種了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們可交流一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算通宵跟我交流種花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞說 今晚我們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一條龍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我很挑客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過看你這麼帥 我也急著用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你來我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…我先去洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你別這樣急色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人先洗也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是兩個人洗澡有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是阿東老闆？你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裏是屯門警署
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩小時前 錦田發生一宗車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}機主當場身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我見你是最後聯絡她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問你是不是認識機主？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在方不方便過來認屍？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽見嗎？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}細雞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥 大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那妞不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 知道… - 走走走…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的禮金呢？忘了在裏面 陪我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}禮金不要了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉的 你踢穿門幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這門開不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大 你先跳樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 老大怎能丟下你不管？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大先跳樓 你馬上跟著來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行 我抽出腳就跟你一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}禮金呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不是為了籌錢給我媽醫病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不會跟你幹這種缺德的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算缺德
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎樣才算？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是送你上小巴了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.33,0:24:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深更半夜很多壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.66,0:24:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙我阿東
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:24:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老娘出來混的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.25,0:25:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你爸還在看蒙面超人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.62,0:25:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.62,0:25:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爆啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.33,0:25:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臭小子 乘人之危
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.83,0:25:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}專欺負無知少女 我警告你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.66,0:25:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次再遇上我 你就沒這樣好運
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.25,0:25:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.25,0:25:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和阿東真的有緣份
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想想 香港有幾百萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們倆會一起假結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是天生一對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等這件事過去後
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.04,0:25:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬤嬤給你們搞一場最浪漫 最美麗的婚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傻丫頭 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 嬤嬤 - 乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.66,0:26:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.00,0:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不結婚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.04,0:26:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 查票
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.54,0:26:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.37,0:26:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.50,0:27:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.58,0:27:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明賣出五張票 怎麼會有七個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.66,0:27:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那兩個人呢？還沒查
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.04,0:27:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不是在做夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就別停
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有靈感了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.75,0:27:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.16,0:27:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.45,0:27:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知道 你現在做每件事我都不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是比我勤力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.29,0:27:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為做得久比我勤力就行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.95,0:27:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是不明白 明白你就坐我位子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在這裏我最大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.91,0:28:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看外面有誰肯幫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.04,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很惱火？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會炒你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會慢慢折磨你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.62,0:28:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也休想辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}負資產怎供樓 露宿街頭呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.50,0:28:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出去幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關門
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.20,0:28:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你女朋友進來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.83,0:28:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梁震找你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你呀 范知進
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把明天開會要用的東西搬上會議室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.45,0:29:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天你不用來了 會議沒你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.41,0:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人搬 別妨礙其他同事工作
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.75,0:29:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電梯又壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走樓梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.83,0:32:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道你想怎樣 你是比我勤力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.33,0:32:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這裏做的也比我久
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.12,0:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會炒你 我會慢慢折磨你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.70,0:32:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼多大廈 想砸死人呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.58,0:32:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.41,0:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你從那座大廈下來是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.54,0:32:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知道 每座大廈的窗門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.37,0:32:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有很多秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都神…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.00,0:33:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.04,0:33:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的是神僊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.16,0:33:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我給你些種子 - 喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.87,0:33:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 開花你就發啦 - 你幹什麼…幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.66,0:33:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神經病
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.66,0:34:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我給你些種子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.41,0:34:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開花你就發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.37,0:36:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.79,0:36:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小子 超重了 出去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 別這麼兇 斯文點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.91,0:36:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}斯文點？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.95,0:36:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在就是你們這些小子搞得香港亂哄哄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不說是你們老不死的在擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.70,0:36:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老不死？信不信我找你媽打醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.04,0:36:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開玩笑 嚇唬我呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就打你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.37,0:36:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打我？吃屎吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敢還手？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.25,0:36:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓一讓…請讓一讓…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.20,0:36:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.83,0:36:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別妨礙警察辦案
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒杯水給你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.33,0:36:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻桃為何會這麼狠？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.29,0:36:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很恐怖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.37,0:37:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是呀 她一刀在頸部割下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.16,0:37:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎能下手？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.70,0:37:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們早回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.00,0:37:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見她拿著老闆送給她的訂情禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.54,0:37:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要退還給他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.87,0:37:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著兩位便在房內吵起來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.20,0:37:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想是老闆求愛不遂而霸王硬上弓
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.20,0:37:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他…強姦我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.45,0:39:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}范知進
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.62,0:39:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不認得我聲音了？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.29,0:40:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…死啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.41,0:40:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王后
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.29,0:40:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看什麼 我又不是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女人好煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.29,0:40:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 如果她喜歡你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是挺可愛…的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.75,0:41:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿進
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.50,0:41:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梁震瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.41,0:41:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他割傷自己的臉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.66,0:41:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從醫院跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不肯放過我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.08,0:41:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他還沒死？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.75,0:41:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這條鑰匙我一直留著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得 我來這裏會安全點
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是我的 你為什麼要走？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.50,0:43:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿進 我報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你見過公司附近的隧道那個乞丐？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.37,0:43:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說 他是公司老員工
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.95,0:44:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被前老闆逼走後就瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.95,0:44:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺多人捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.62,0:44:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.95,0:45:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兒童圖書裏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.00,0:45:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多時候 王子和公主都有美滿結局
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.45,0:45:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但現實是不是這樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.04,0:45:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這問是我的祖屋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.12,0:45:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是我成為插畫家的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.50,0:51:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 陳老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.16,0:51:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 對不起 我最近有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.37,0:51:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道 但真的有點私人事情
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.45,0:51:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能再給我幾天時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.37,0:51:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會盡快給你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.33,0:51:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.16,0:51:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.95,0:54:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.04,0:54:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很驚喜吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.79,0:54:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我不好 遲了給你慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.62,0:54:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在給你補上 你別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.79,0:54:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我生日那天你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.50,0:54:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你說過嘛 我陪了一個客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.33,0:54:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你陪的不是客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.50,0:54:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟她沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.45,0:54:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她有錢可以幫我 就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.33,0:54:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且那次以後 我再沒見過她了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.33,0:54:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什麼都看見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.37,0:55:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什麼都看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.04,0:55:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.87,0:55:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這十年來 我這樣辛苦為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.16,0:55:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不是為了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.87,0:55:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道就沒回轉餘地？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.62,0:55:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不過做錯了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.91,0:55:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你幫了我不少
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.54,0:55:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我在外面真的欠了人家很多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.20,0:55:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想你再勉強接那麼多工作
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.08,0:55:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.04,0:55:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.33,0:55:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆 你再幫我這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這房子 反正你很久都沒回來住
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.87,0:55:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賣掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.25,0:55:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賣掉它 我們可以像以前那樣開心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.04,0:55:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說沒見過她？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.00,0:56:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒見過她 這香水味從哪裏來？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.75,0:56:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在哄我賣房子 好讓你有錢花？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.16,0:56:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底騙了我多少次？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.75,0:56:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你騙了我多少次 你說 - 你發什麼瘋
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.12,0:56:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你別這樣 老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.87,0:56:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發瘋是嗎 你走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.70,0:56:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.87,0:56:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.95,1:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.58,1:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好想你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.12,1:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你在這
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.29,1:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你出來見我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.16,1:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.12,1:05:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄧祁山 你想怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.37,1:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.87,1:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.50,1:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這地方這麼值錢你都不賣
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.12,1:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會痛 很快的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.37,1:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄧祁山你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.37,1:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.70,1:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見 老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.00,1:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我 你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.54,1:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乖女
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.04,1:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.16,1:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽沒有好好照顧你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.83,1:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裏面那男人這樣對你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.37,1:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會放過他
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.66,1:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.08,1:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.58,1:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別丟下我…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.12,1:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.33,1:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這工廠是我婆婆留給我媽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.00,1:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我媽再留給我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.62,1:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做自己喜歡做的事有什麼問題？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.54,1:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 你愛打棉胎你自己打個夠
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.45,1:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打到死那天我也不會再理你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.25,1:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要騙我
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.54,1:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你外面有女人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.29,1:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神經病 我不跟你囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.41,1:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.25,1:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}著火啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.79,1:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.50,1:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來 王子是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.54,1:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在千鈞一髮時 病危的母后及時趕到
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.95,1:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后拚死和魔鬼同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.79,1:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偉大的母愛終於救了小公主
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.58,1:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彤彤 你肯回來孤兒院教書
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.58,1:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.58,1:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.70,1:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}院長
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.25,1:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這本是我畫的新作 送給你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.87,1:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.37,1:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.37,1:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.41,1:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關二哥在上 我們五子遭逢厄運
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.29,1:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要有一位死士 以身犯險
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.91,1:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}懇請關二哥 抽這位死士出來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.41,1:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜過關二哥 大家莫囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.62,1:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟關二哥不太熟
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.41,1:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只知道他喜歡聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.25,1:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在去廁所再唱
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.04,1:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰慢誰吃虧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.45,1:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明說好抽籤
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.87,1:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搶什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.12,1:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是 現在還不是一人一枝？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.20,1:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浪費口水
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.54,1:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家拿出來對一對
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.29,1:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰人抽了死簽？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.66,1:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼死簽？都一樣長
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.04,1:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有說過比長短嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.41,1:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嚇？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.83,1:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.20,1:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.83,1:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.04,1:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我扭不了？為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.16,1:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就扭得了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.95,1:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.75,1:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大老闆 我們抽了生死簽了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.29,1:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關二哥決定 阿聰走東城線
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.04,1:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.00,1:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關二哥？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.75,1:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我推翻這個決定
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.00,1:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們是一間大公司
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.41,1:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼能用這種迷信的方式呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.70,1:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我決定…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.08,1:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}投票
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.58,1:11:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就你了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.37,1:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們先出去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.04,1:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.50,1:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.45,1:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東城戲院那條線 停了十幾年呀
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.12,1:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.75,1:11:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東城電影院 以前是個殯儀館嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.86,1:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道還要我去？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.50,1:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿聰 我跟你講
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.62,1:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們可以來一個…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.04,1:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"撞鬼自遊行"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.50,1:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刺激呀 我把他們一車一車的拉去撞鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}錢就一車一車的來
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.54,1:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們還集資上市幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.16,1:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱們直奔納斯達克
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.66,1:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自游不行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.95,1:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不知道 好多前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.25,1:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去了那邊 都…失蹤呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.91,1:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}司機找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.79,1:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他老婆對他不好 離家出走
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.20,1:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.37,1:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你前幾天是不是請假？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.24,1:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要去參加什麼唱歌比賽？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.87,1:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對呀 對呀 參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.77,1:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買個新吉他 三萬多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.06,1:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去不上了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.29,1:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.16,1:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我不給你假呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.16,1:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老闆呀 你給我機會呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.66,1:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道我唱歌多好聽啊 我唱給你聽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.22,1:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是否你唯一的粉腸
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.45,1:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.45,1:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感動
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.00,1:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好不好聽？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.12,1:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好聽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.83,1:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.25,1:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難受 你…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.41,1:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你到底是想窮死 還是想嚇死？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.41,1:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我這個人 是個公平 公正 公開的人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.79,1:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裏有個球
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.33,1:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把它投進籃裏
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.58,1:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我贏
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.45,1:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去東城
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.75,1:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我投不進去呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.91,1:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你贏
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.66,1:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不去 好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.33,1:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.16,1:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以的 來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.95,1:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝老闆
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.50,1:13:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣也投不進去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.95,1:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老闆 你好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老闆好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.41,1:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了減低公司損失的風險
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.91,1:14:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們精心挑選公司最破的一輛車
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.75,1:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去迎接這個九死一生的任務
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.54,1:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的捨不得…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.41,1:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這輛車
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.00,1:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.33,1:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我送個對話機給你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.16,1:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.00,1:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二十四小時都要保持聯絡
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.45,1:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕萬一你有什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.54,1:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起碼我們也知道 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.16,1:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家屬謝禮
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.50,1:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.29,1:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.37,1:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"南無阿彌陀佛…"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.04,1:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 換別的音樂行不行？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.62,1:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.29,1:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 開
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.58,1:16:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 真的十五個五？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.00,1:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢材 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.33,1:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我蠢？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.58,1:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿聰一把年紀 還在做歌星夢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.12,1:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他才真蠢呀
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.91,1:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少廢話 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.87,1:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喝就喝
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.66,1:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 再來
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.78,1:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.41,1:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回應一下好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.15,1:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.54,1:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.66,1:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 來點動靜呀
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.73,1:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂喂 別鬧了 真的怕
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.83,1:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥 真害怕呀
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.29,1:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有個阿婆在車上
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.54,1:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.91,1:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.37,1:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.29,1:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是腎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.20,1:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下面是屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.41,1:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿婆 你別亂戳
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.50,1:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是說 這是什麼站呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.75,1:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是東院墳場
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.87,1:17:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿婆 你想在哪裏下車？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.04,1:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我到家啦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.87,1:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嚇得我…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.45,1:18:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小伙子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.41,1:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.91,1:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你車上有髒東西
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.12,1:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你自己小心呀
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.79,1:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼多家人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.20,1:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都出來等
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.66,1:18:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事吧 阿婆？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.87,1:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住這裏？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.91,1:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬這麼高 回天國？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.20,1:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心跳出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.16,1:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.33,1:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們這些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.16,1:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有瓶子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣瞧得起我 這麼窄？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.25,1:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.62,1:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窄點也好 試試
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.20,1:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.62,1:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼窄用不得 有進無出
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.79,1:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.54,1:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.91,1:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.66,1:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 我的媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.62,1:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有怪莫怪 小孩尿急尿過界
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.62,1:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.00,1:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.54,1:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}按不住啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.41,1:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你個混蛋 在我花園尿尿？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.75,1:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.58,1:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}司機大哥 滿地都是水 怎麼搞的？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.45,1:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨便啦 又沒讓你喝
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.87,1:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好面熟
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.62,1:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪裏見過呢？看著我
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.04,1:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒見過帥哥呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.62,1:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.00,1:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還讓你認出來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.41,1:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我認得你啦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.20,1:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一把年紀 年年都參加歌唱比賽
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.62,1:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年年都怯場的那位大叔？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.66,1:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才一把年紀
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.62,1:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來你開巴士？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.25,1:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很失禮你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.29,1:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 我記得你唱那首歌
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.41,1:20:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好正點 這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.87,1:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"我是否你唯一的粉腸"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.91,1:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱夠沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.12,1:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的很趣致 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.29,1:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滾開吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.70,1:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒人看見 玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.62,1:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 你車上有髒東西
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.33,1:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也看到了？快走
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.66,1:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.62,1:21:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.41,1:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.63,1:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你哭什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.12,1:22:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她掐住我傷口
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.83,1:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭了 男人老狗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.79,1:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們在哪裏下車呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.58,1:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去總站 東城戲院
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.83,1:22:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真以為我們是女鬼呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.79,1:22:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們是樂隊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.50,1:22:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是來參加化妝舞會
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.66,1:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是為了慶祝這巴士線重開而舉辦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.20,1:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧 快些和我們一起進場玩
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.91,1:22:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.41,1:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地板那麼髒 有人嘔吐就找人清潔呀
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.79,1:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走吧 遲到啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.08,1:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改天吧 你…你先走
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.45,1:22:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.95,1:23:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你先走 改天再約
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.41,1:23:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別這樣 可以上台唱歌 你唱得那麼好聽
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.45,1:23:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別耍我了 我哪會唱歌
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.62,1:23:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要謙虛 你唱歌很好聽
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.66,1:23:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.66,1:23:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱什麼歌？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.04,1:23:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱什麼歌？我們給你伴奏
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.75,1:23:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們給你伴奏？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.87,1:23:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎那麼囉嗦？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.91,1:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼歌呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.75,1:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.25,1:23:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰唱的？沒聽過？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.70,1:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快開始了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.45,1:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入場啦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.41,1:24:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"都黐咗線走火入魔 鬼怪甚多"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.75,1:24:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"問你怕不怕"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.25,1:24:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"哎呀弊啦 佢扮傻（佢系堅傻）"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.83,1:24:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"驚乜鬼一於少理繼續唱歌"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.79,1:24:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"唱到勁跳熱舞 齊齊變成舞王 八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.70,1:25:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"世界話變就變 人人芝麻開門 八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.70,1:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"八個十個伴唱 齊齊唱齊唱齊"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.16,1:25:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"繼續唱 繼續跳 八步八步八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.12,1:25:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"咁鬼人齊 應該皆大歡喜"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.58,1:25:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"但系點解你地個個都好似就死"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.41,1:25:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"有啲黐埋一坺"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.20,1:25:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"其他甩頭甩脾"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.70,1:25:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"醫番好都嘥氣"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.16,1:25:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"叫曬佢地番屋企"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.91,1:25:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"點算左眼好似望到孖女齊坐"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.33,1:25:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"望下似幻覺"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.83,1:25:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"哎呀弊啦 我系傻（繫個呀婆）"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.41,1:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"驚乜鬼驚都嘥氣繼續唱歌"
